g.title: j2750000439
g.text: Arthur says you owe him a drink

g.title: j2554594291
g.text: You seem upset. Is it something I said?

g.title: j2299833150
g.text: cause I told him we both think he sucks for making fun of me being an On-lyne fan ^_^

g.title: j2425200176
g.text: Good! He's not getting that drink.

g.title: j1206378172
g.text: Oh you really told him that? Hah.

g.title: j3695376068
g.text: Tell him he can shove it.

g.title: j1941351508
g.text: Tell him he owes *me* a drink for putting up with him.

g.title: j1232120319
g.text: I didn't love being called boring.

g.title: j2620732581
g.text: is this like a fun tit-for-tat thing or like an actual frustration thing?

g.title: j3927157762
g.text: Oh. I really didn't mean anything by it.

g.title: j4261554447
g.text: Well, thanks for the heads up.

g.title: j2365778672
g.text: So, what is the deal between the two of you?

g.title: j2517682328
g.text: Nah, it's fine. Just having an off day.

g.title: j1730316827
g.text: I just have a lot going on, but that's true for all of us.

g.title: j2041165744
g.text: It's all good fun, don't worry haha

g.title: j756863492
g.text: take ur frustration out on the bad guys! that's what I do ;)

g.title: j627343892
g.text: gosh. mean humor is so confusing

g.title: j3000914784
g.text: Honest. I'm sorry I upset you.

g.title: j3397319253
g.text: You're not boring, Aoi. I just thought I was being clever.

g.title: j1029773535
g.text: If you were really boring, I wouldn't be talking to you.

g.title: j220210856
g.text: but u know, there really is a lot weighing on u. That might be true for all of us, but it doesn’t make ur experience any less real

g.title: j1515553031
g.text: It seems the jury's convinced by your defense

g.title: j3976190551
g.text: I just hope u know it’s okay to have off days

g.title: j1881683635
g.text: nah but it's cool if it's yours!

g.title: j1711009423
g.text: so... if the intent is to show the person you like them u tell them u don't like them?

g.title: j2393142265
g.text: and grants you a fresh start

g.title: j2311461377
g.text: Does that mean what I think it means?

g.title: j263863448
g.text: Sounds like you might be speaking from experience.

g.title: j1833895374
g.text: Making a mental note not to joke around with you like that then.

g.title: j3010019339
g.text: Good, because I'm definitely going to joke around with you like that.

g.title: j1854958329
g.text: It only works if everyone knows each other well enough to understand where the lines are. Getting close to the line without crossing it shows you’re comfortable with each other.

g.title: j3642539813
g.text: ha. u ever met anyone who arrived in Höllvania emotionally stable?

g.title: j3563249691
g.text: u and Arthur are more alike aaall the tiiime

g.title: j235584941
g.text: I appreciate your very clinical explanation of how comedy works

g.title: j1277187148
g.text: that is hella confusing to me

g.title: j377657138
g.text: Oh, I see Aoi's emoticons are back. I think that's a good sign.

g.title: j1685111304
g.text: let's just say Arthur and I have been strictly professional since On-lyne's second world tour

g.title: j1353339106
g.text: I’ll just leave it at that

g.title: j1374282396
g.text: :) I like u more all the time

g.title: j1134250097
g.text: Is that meant to be a compliment?

g.title: j1828126907
g.text: I thought mean humor wasn't your style ;)

g.title: j4156303715
g.text: but what matters is it makes sense to you and Arthur!

g.title: j2071727807
g.text: You want to to tell me how Arthur screwed that up?

g.title: j154317858
g.text: You're more insightful than you let on.

g.title: j1161249283
g.text: All right, we'll leave it at that.

g.title: j1450477636
g.text: I bet you say that to all the time travellers.

g.title: j2636061777
g.text: Arthur really does want that drink tho lol

g.title: j2704958230
g.text: that's a tale for another day

g.title: j532659324
g.text: I hope he knows he's not getting it. ;)

g.title: j3923708387
g.text: And what do you want? You're saving people all the time too.

g.title: j3646459422
g.text: and a few too many drinks

g.title: j2854626796
g.text: a girl's gotta have her secrets

g.title: j4155996361
g.text: thx for caring about us in the hex. it doesn't go unnoticed. really.

g.title: j4062632008
g.text: don't let Arthur give you too much trouble, k?

g.title: j2596562081
g.text: Hey, you don't have to tell me anything you don't want to tell me.

g.title: j2977526330
g.text: I'd settle for a new stereo and world peace

g.title: j2023795990
g.text: I'll see what I can do.

g.title: j3495998431
g.text: in the wise words of Drillbit, "dream big. then hustle."
